OL,4,CIndigenous schools: Trudeau tells
OL,5,CCatholic Church to 'take
OL,6,Cresponsibility'
OL,7, Canadian Prime Minister Justin Trudeau
OL,8, has urged the Catholic Church to "take
OL,9, responsibility" for its role in
OL,10, indigenous residential schools.
OL,12,FThe remains of 215 children were found
OL,13,Fburied in one school last month,
OL,14,Fprompting nationwide outrage.
OL,16,FMr Trudeau said requests for the Church
OL,17,Fto release its records on the schools
OL,18,Fhad been met with "resistance".
